      "role": "user",
      "content": "that silence... yeah. it's exactly that. it's like the noise of trying to find a reason to keep driving just... stops. it's actually kind of peaceful. like, once you accept that there aren't any more stops left on the route, you don't have to fight the engine anymore.",
